-- Roche could buy small or medium sized company: CEO
-- 
-- Wed Feb 7, 2007 7:01am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/07/us-roche-results-ceo-idUSZAT00606020070207

 

 BASEL, Switzerland  (Reuters) - Swiss drugmaker Roche ( ROG.VX ) could buy a smaller or medium sized company if the opportunity arose, the company's chief executive said on Wednesday. 


 "We have the money there available should the opportunity present itself," Roche CEO Franz Humer told reporters in Basel. "The money is there for smaller and medium sized acquisitions," he said.